702487f-a.title: Brooklyn: 9th Street - 5th Avenue
702487f-a.text:
9th Street, east from (No. 287) near and across Fifth
Avenue, showing the B. M. T. elevated station on the latter.
At number 291 is the Avon Theatre, and at the corner of Fifth
Avenue is the Michaels Brothers furniture house. View 2 is
east from Fifth Avenue.
June 14, 1940
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr  (6 3 8  -eg, 339
NO REPRODUCTIONS
